<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a18Dec1923"><font color="red">18 December 1923</font> <i>STA</i> (to Lily Bollach): Here is the copy of my novel which I ought to have brought yesterday &hellip; I shall inflict some more MS on you in a few days but in case it is not before the 25th allow me to wish you a happy Christmas. </div>
